title: Does President Trump's proposal exclude military votes overseas in the Florida elections?
subtitle: If this is done, the President ' s call for the completion of the results of the initial elections before 16 November will exclude the ballot papers cast by Floridaans abroad.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: If President Donald Tramp ' s proposal of 12 November to finalize the results of the night elections for two competitions in Florida is implemented, the ballot papers sent abroad by United States military personnel will be excluded.
